  this  enhancement  of  eligibility  limits  does not make any difference considering the inflation and consequent rise in the wages of the employees over the years since the last amendment was  made   almost all the central trade unions have demanded for the removal of conditions on payment of  ceiling  and  eligibility  limits  in  a  series  of  meeting  with  the  government    i request the government to reconsider their demand in this regard and bring about a fresh  amendment  on  the  payment  of  bonus  act  to  remove  all  conditions  on payment of ceiling and eligibility limits    